#! categorical operations, but only as set-theoretic operations.

#! @Description
#! The arguments are a monomorphism $\iota: k \hookrightarrow a$
#! and a morphism $\tau: t \rightarrow a$
#! such that there is a morphism $u: t \rightarrow k$ with
